OL,3,CBarnaby Webber's family help unveil
OL,4,CKnife Angel statue
OL,6,FEmma Webber told ITV News' knife crime
OL,7,Fneeds to be addressed urgently.
OL,9,FA statue made out of 100,000 knives
OL,10,Fcollected by police forces has been
OL,11,Funveiled in Taunton by the relatives
OL,12,Fof two victims of violence.
OL,14,FThe Knife Angel will spend a month in
OL,15,Fthe town centre as part of a
OL,16,Fnationwide tour.
OL,18,FEmma Webber, mum of Barnaby Webber,
OL,19,Fwho was killed in a knife attack in
OL,20,FNottingham in 2023, was one of those
OL,21,Fwho spoke at the ceremony.
