OL,3,CBarnaby Webber's family help unveil
OL,4,CKnife Angel statue
OL,6,FAdam Fouracre also spoke at the event.
OL,7,FHis brother, Lloyd Fouracre, was
OL,8,Fkilled in a violent attack in Taunton
OL,9,Fin 2005.
OL,11,FThe statue, which aims to raise
OL,12,Fawareness of the negative effects of
OL,13,Fviolence and aggression, stands at 27
OL,14,Fft tall, weighs 3.5 tonnes and is made
OL,15,Fout of knives and blades retrieved
OL,16,Ffrom amnesty bins from across all 43
OL,17,FUK police forces.
OL,19,FIt was designed by artist, Alfie
OL,20,FBradley at the British Ironwork Centre.
