OL,6,FAdam Fouracre founded Stand Against
OL,7,FViolence after his brother, Lloyd, was
OL,8,Fkilled.
OL,10,FHe said: "It is a terrific opportunity
OL,11,Fto be involved in supporting the Knife
OL,12,FAngel project in Somerset where my
OL,13,Fbrother lost his life to mindless
OL,14,Fviolence.
OL,16,F"The Knife Angel doesn't just
OL,17,Frepresent the victims who have lost
OL,18,Ftheir lives to knife attacks but to
OL,19,Fall victims of violent acts.
