OL,6,F"We still have a long way to go to see
OL,7,Fan end to violence in this country,
OL,8,Fbut it begins with awareness and
OL,9,Feducation - something that we hope the
OL,10,FKnife Angel will bring and that we can
OL,11,Fabsolutely support."
OL,13,FThe Webber family have also welcomed
OL,14,Fthe arrival of the Knife Angel.
OL,16,FBarnaby's Mum, Emma said: "We are
OL,17,Fstill trying to process the
OL,18,Fdevastating loss of our beautiful boy.
