OL,6,F"The cruel and senseless way that he
OL,7,Fwas taken from us and denied his
OL,8,Fbright future, hurts every single day.
OL,9,FViolent crimes, especially knife
OL,10,Fcrime, are at an epidemic level in our
OL,11,Fcountry and is something that must be
OL,12,Faddressed urgently.
OL,14,F"We are glad to offer any support that
OL,15,Fwe can in ensuring this impactful,
OL,16,Fimportant and educational visit serves
OL,17,Fits purpose.
